# Data Property: <http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos#notation> (notation)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos#notation> "By convention, skos:notation is used with a typed literal in the object position of the triple."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos#notation> <http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos#notation> "notation"@en)



